edu.umd.cs.psl.model.formula.traversal

Class AbstractFormulaTraverser

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.formula.traversal.AbstractFormulaTraverser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormulaTraverser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Formula2SQL, FormulaEvaluator, FormulaGrounder

    public abstract class AbstractFormulaTraverser
extends java.lang.Object
implements FormulaTraverser
    Implements the depth-first traversal of a formula, but performs no actions during traversal.

    Derived classes can extend this class to implement desired outcomes from traversal.

    Sub-Formulas contained in a Conjunction or a Disjunction are traversed in order from lowest index to highest.
